                     <interp inst="t17610625-31-person286" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live in Cow-cross, I have<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="176106250035"></xptr> known the prisoner upwards of four years, I am his next door neighbour, I believe him to be a very honest man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17610625-31-person287">
                  John 
                  Delany 
               <interp inst="t17610625-31-person287" type="surname" value="Delany"></interp>
